title: Diary
content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:Diary
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.

Diary may refer to:

  • Achievement Diaries
    • Ardougne Diary
    • Desert Diary
    • Falador Diary
    • Fremennik Diary
    • Kandarin Diary
    • Karamja Diary
    • Kourend & Kebos Diary
    • Lumbridge & Draynor Diary
    • Morytania Diary
    • Varrock Diary
    • Western Provinces Diary
    • Wilderness Diary

Items[edit | edit source]

  • Items named "Diary":
    • Diary (Horror from the Deep), a book from the Lighthouse
    • Diary (Shades of Mort'ton), a diary written by Herbi Flax from the Shades of Mort'ton quest
    • Diary (Witch's House) from the Witch's House quest
  • Aivas' diary, obtained from searching the skeleton by the Lithkren Vault entrance
  • Ancient diary, obtained from the House on the Hill
  • Archaeologist's diary, obtained from searching Charles Charlington in the Tar Swamp
  • Atlax's diary, obtained from searching the Rewards Guardian
  • Bloody diary, obtained from the Prifddinas Grand Library
  • Burnt diary, a quest item from Royal Trouble
  • Grim reaper's diary, a holiday event item from the 2014 Halloween event
  • Entomologist's diary, obtained from searching the entomologist in the Kalphite Cave
  • Houndmaster's diary, obtained after defeating the Muttadiles
  • Ohn's diary, obtained from searching a crate in Zul-Andra
  • Old diary, obtained during A Taste of Hope
  • Ricktor's diary (7), obtained from the Arceuus Library
  • Rose's diary, obtained during A Kingdom Divided
  • Serafina's diary, obtained from a bookshelf after defeating Verzik Vitur
  • Sin'keth's diary from the What Lies Below quest
  • Tarn's diary from Tarn's Lair
